---
name: Full Deploy
version: 2.0.0
description: Full deployment with all block types
owners: [platform-team, sre-team]
environments: [staging, production]
requires:
  tools: [kubectl, jq]
  permissions: [k8s:deploy]
  approvals:
    production: [tech-lead]
timeout: 30m
---

# Full Deploy

## Prerequisites

```check name="cluster-healthy"
kubectl get nodes | grep -c Ready | test $(cat) -ge 3
```

```check name="no-incidents"
curl -s https://status.internal/api/active | jq '.count == 0'
```

## Deploy

```step name="migrate-db" rollback="rollback-db"
  timeout: 300s
  confirm: production
  env: [staging, production]
---
./scripts/migrate.sh --env={{env}} --version={{version}}
```

```rollback name="rollback-db"
./scripts/migrate.sh --env={{env}} --rollback
```

```step name="deploy-app" depends_on="migrate-db" rollback="rollback-app"
  timeout: 600s
---
kubectl set image deployment/api api={{image}}:{{version}}
kubectl rollout status deployment/api --timeout=120s
```

```rollback name="rollback-app"
kubectl rollout undo deployment/api
```

## Monitor

```wait name="canary-watch" duration="300s"
  abort_if: error_rate > 1%
---
./scripts/monitor-canary.sh --threshold=1%
```

## Verify

```step name="smoke-test" depends_on="deploy-app"
curl -sf http://api.{{env}}.svc.cluster.local/health
```
